        "text": "<p>Today, Lydia's vision and passion is shared with her husband, David, Co-Founder and Chief Operating Officer, and daughter Shiri Sarfati, Executive Vice President and Chief Marketing Officer. They oversee a 50,000 square foot, ISO 9001:2015 certified, manufacturing, research, development and training facility in Secaucus, NJ. Repêchage is now the leading professional skincare brand based on seaweed, combining natural ingredients with high tech research and development, utilizing a proprietary seaweed extraction method that yields the highest quality seaweed that is used in all the company's products and treatments.<\/p>",
